  "CARD_EDITOR.tooltip.statefulTransformReturnCount": "Choose the history, pile, card, orb, or status condition that transforms this card back.",
  "CARD_EDITOR.tooltip.statefulTransformReturnMatch": "Optional second condition that transforms the card back. This uses the same history/count matcher as other effects.",
